@startuml ThetaGang Income Sources
!theme toy
skinparam linetype ortho

title ThetaGang 净收益来源分解

skinparam rectangle {
  BackgroundColor #F0F8FF
  BorderColor #4169E1
}

skinparam arrow {
  Color #4169E1
}

rectangle "净收益 (Net Income)" as NI #98FB98 {

  rectangle "权利金收入 (Premium Income)" as PI #FFD700 {
    card "卖出看跌期权" as CSP
    card "卖出备兑看涨期权" as CC
  }

  rectangle "资本利得 (Capital Gains)" as CG #87CEEB {
    card "低买高卖股票" as STOCK
    card "行权价-成本价差" as DIFF
  }

  rectangle "其他收益" as OI #DDA0DD {
    card "已实现盈亏" as RP
  }
}

NI --> PI
NI --> CG
NI --> OI

note bottom of NI
  净收益 = Σ权利金 + Σ股票价差 + Σ已实现盈亏
end note

note bottom of CSP
  Cash Secured Put
  股价>行权价 = 获得全部权利金
  股价<行权价 = 需买入股票
end note

note bottom of CC
  Covered Call
  需先持有股票
  股价<行权价 = 保留权利金+股票
  股价>行权价 = 卖出股票+权利金
end note

@enduml
